                <h1>McDonald's Logo: The Golden Arches Explained</h1>
                <p>The McDonald's logo, featuring the iconic golden arches, is one of the most recognizable symbols in the world. Created in 1962, it embodies the essence of fast food and American culture. The logo's bold colors and simple design create a sense of familiarity and comfort, making it a favorite among millions of customers globally.</p>
